To install Selenium in virtual environment...
1. activate the virtual environment
2. pip or pip3 install selenium==version
3. download the geckodriver for the OS version
4. chmod +x geckodriver
5. put the geckodriver in the /usr/bin folder of the system and bin folder of the virtual environment
6. in the python script:
    from selenium import webdriver
    browser = webdriver.Firefox(executable_path="/path/to/bin/geckodriver")
    # browser = webdriver.Firefox()
